        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Smarter Approaches to Nuclear Expenditures Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill imposes prohibitions and limitations on funding for various Department of Defense (DOD) and Department of Energy (DOE) weapons programs.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Weapons subjected to prohibitions or limitations under this bill include Columbia-class submarines, intercontinental ballistic missiles, low-yield nuclear warheads, and space-based missile defense systems.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The bill also requires various reports to Congress, including a joint report from DOD and DOE outlining the estimated cost savings resulting from this bill.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;!--tinycomments|2.1|data:application/json;base64,--&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
